WEBVTT

00:05.476 --> 00:08.639
OKAY, I´M HERE.
 HAVE YOU FOUND CARMEN YET?

00:08.639 --> 00:10.141
NO, AND I´M WORRIED SICK.

00:10.141 --> 00:12.012
IT´S HER FIRST DAY
 AT A NEW SCHOOL.

00:12.012 --> 00:13.244
SHE SHOULD HAVE BEEN
 HOME AN HOUR AGO.

00:13.244 --> 00:14.785
COME ON, IT´S AN HOUR.

00:14.785 --> 00:17.017
SHE´S GOT NO MONEY.
 SHE´S GOT NO FRIENDS.

00:18.449 --> 00:22.293
SHE´S PROBABLY WALKING AROUND
 THE MALL CRYING.

00:22.293 --> 00:25.596
GEORGE, SHE´S THE NEW KID
 IN CLASS.

00:25.596 --> 00:27.328
SHE´S PROBABLY DEPRESSED.

00:27.328 --> 00:30.201
SHE SHOULD BE HERE AT HOME
 WHERE WE CAN SUPPORT HER.

00:30.201 --> 00:32.803
LET´S SAY SHE DID HAVE A BAD
 DAY -- THE WORST OF HER LIFE.

00:32.803 --> 00:34.465
SHE´S GONNA COME HOME.

00:34.465 --> 00:36.667
SHE´S GONNA TELL US ALL HER
 WORRIES AND ALL HER FEARS.

00:36.667 --> 00:39.740
ISN´T IT BETTER TO LET
 THE HOT-DOG-ON-A-STICK PEOPLE

00:39.740 --> 00:43.544
DEAL WITH THE FIRST FIVE MINUTES
 OF, "SCHOOL! HAIR! BOYS!

00:43.544 --> 00:46.647
NOBODY LIKES ME!"

00:46.647 --> 00:48.379
DAD, HOW COME YOU´RE HOME?

00:48.379 --> 00:49.820
YOUR MOM´S WORRIED

00:49.820 --> 00:52.553
THAT CARMEN´S NOT GONNA MAKE
 ANY FRIENDS AT ALLENDALE,

00:52.553 --> 00:55.286
AND THE KIDS ARE GONNA HARASS
 HER LIKE AT HER OLD SCHOOL.

00:55.286 --> 00:58.429
WHAT IF ALL THE KIDS LIKED HER
 AND EVERYTHING WENT GREAT?

00:58.429 --> 00:59.660
[ LAUGHS ]

00:59.660 --> 01:01.262
[ LAUGHS ]

01:01.262 --> 01:03.294
COME ON, WHAT ARE THE ODDS?

01:03.294 --> 01:05.596
HI! SORRY I´M LATE.

01:05.596 --> 01:07.738
YOU KNOW,
 YOU COULD HAVE CALLED.

01:07.738 --> 01:09.200
WHO´S THIS?

01:09.200 --> 01:11.372
EVERYONE, THIS IS MY NEW
 FRIEND, OLIVIA.

01:11.372 --> 01:13.674
HEY, WE CAN SEE THIS ONE.

01:13.674 --> 01:15.376
MAX, BE POLITE.

01:15.376 --> 01:17.648
CARMEN HAS A NEW FRIEND.

01:17.648 --> 01:20.651
A FRIEND, GEORGE --
 A NEW FRIEND.

01:20.651 --> 01:22.283
I HAD THE BEST DAY.

01:22.283 --> 01:24.455
I KNOW IT´S GONNA BE
 TOUGH TO CATCH UP,

01:24.455 --> 01:26.217
BUT AT LEAST I MET OLIVIA.

01:26.217 --> 01:28.389
SHE´S STARTING
 MIDSEMESTER, TOO.

01:28.389 --> 01:30.761
SO, WHAT ARE YOU IN FOR?

01:30.761 --> 01:32.723
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

01:32.723 --> 01:35.596
LOOK, YOU CHANGED SCHOOLS IN
 THE MIDDLE OF THE YEAR.

01:35.596 --> 01:37.468
I MEAN, IT´S OKAY.
 WE DON´T JUDGE.

01:37.468 --> 01:40.371
BUT WHAT IS IT --
 YOU KNOW, TWEAKER, KLEPTO?

01:40.371 --> 01:44.235
YOU GOT A BUN IN THE OVEN?

01:44.235 --> 01:45.476
NO.

01:45.476 --> 01:47.378
I´M FROM TORONTO.

01:47.378 --> 01:49.340
LIKE I SAID, WE DON´T JUDGE.

01:52.443 --> 01:53.614
HI. I´M MAX.

01:53.614 --> 01:55.616
CAN I GET YOU SOMETHING
 TO DRINK?

01:55.616 --> 01:57.418
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

01:57.418 --> 01:59.450
SHE´S A GUEST.

02:00.621 --> 02:02.323
I´LL COOK YOU THINGS.

02:02.323 --> 02:04.825
YOU SMELL GOOD.
 I BET BEES CHASE YOU.

02:06.126 --> 02:08.329
YOU´RE SO CUTE.
 HOW OLD ARE YOU?

02:08.329 --> 02:11.802
SEE ALL THESE TEETH?
 PERMANENT.

02:11.802 --> 02:14.235
OKAY, OLIVIA, WHY DON´T WE GO
 START STUDYING?

02:14.235 --> 02:16.237
MY ROOM IS THE FIRST ONE
 TO THE LEFT.

02:16.237 --> 02:17.468
OKAY.

02:17.468 --> 02:19.710
I´D BETTER START
 MY HOMEWORK, TOO.

02:19.710 --> 02:21.342
DAD, HOW COULD YOU?

02:21.342 --> 02:24.615
TWEAKER, MY ONE FRIEND,
 NEW SCHOOL, TORONTO,

02:24.615 --> 02:26.377
BUN IN THE OVEN?!

02:31.352 --> 02:34.455
I DID IT, ANGIE.
 I DID IT.

02:34.455 --> 02:36.357
I TUNED HER OUT.

02:38.289 --> 02:40.191
AFTER ALL THESE YEARS
 OF PRACTICING.

02:40.191 --> 02:42.333
QUICK, SAY SOMETHING TO ME.

02:42.333 --> 02:43.594
THAT´S NOT FUNNY.

02:43.594 --> 02:46.237
WHAT?

02:46.237 --> 02:47.838
YES!

02:49.770 --> 02:52.773
CARSON CITY IS
 THE CAPITAL OF NEVADA.

02:52.773 --> 02:55.175
CONCORD IS THE CAPITAL OF
 NEW HAMPSHIRE.

02:55.175 --> 02:58.178
AND TRENTON IS
 THE CAPITAL OF NEW JERSEY,

02:58.178 --> 03:00.281
ALSO KNOWN AS
 THE GARDEN STATE!

03:00.281 --> 03:02.313
I LOVE YOU!

03:04.615 --> 03:07.358
HEY, BEFORE I FORGET, GIVE ME
 YOUR CELLPHONE NUMBER

03:07.358 --> 03:09.290
SO WE CAN TEXT-MESSAGE
 EACH OTHER IN CLASS.

03:09.290 --> 03:11.262
I´M NOT ALLOWED TO HAVE
 A CELLPHONE.

03:11.262 --> 03:13.694
WHAT IF SOMEONE TRIED TO
 KIDNAP YOU OR SOMETHING?

03:13.694 --> 03:16.967
MY DAD SAYS HIS TAXES PAY
 FOR THE AMBER ALERTS.

03:30.381 --> 03:33.744
[ GASPS ] DID YOU SEE THAT BOY
 MATT WHO CAME INTO HOMEROOM?

03:33.744 --> 03:35.846
OH, MY GOD.
 HE´S A FULL-ON DIME.

03:35.846 --> 03:37.488
OH, FORGET IT.

03:37.488 --> 03:39.650
DO YOU HAVE A SHIRT
 I CAN BORROW?

03:39.650 --> 03:41.752
I WANT TO GET OUT OF
 THIS UNIFORM.

03:41.752 --> 03:44.425
YEAH, SURE.

03:52.503 --> 03:54.365
HERE, TRY THIS.

03:55.566 --> 03:58.709
SO, WHAT DO YOU THINK
 OF MY LITTLE BROTHER?

03:58.709 --> 04:00.471
OH, HE´S ADORABLE.

04:00.471 --> 04:02.943
YEAH, TOO BAD ABOUT
 HIS EYE.

04:02.943 --> 04:04.845
WHAT´S WRONG WITH HIS EYE?

04:06.377 --> 04:08.319
AAH!

04:08.319 --> 04:10.551
[ INTRO TO WAR´S "LOW RIDER"
 PLAYS ]

04:21.462 --> 04:26.767
♫ ALL MY FRIENDS
 KNOW THE LOW RIDER ♫

04:55.896 --> 04:58.329
HE WAS LOOKING AT OLIVIA
 THROUGH A PEEPHOLE.

04:58.329 --> 05:01.001
HE WAS WATCHING HER CHANGE UNTIL
 I SPRAYED HIM WITH THE PERFUME.

05:01.001 --> 05:02.433
THAT´S NOT TRUE!

05:02.433 --> 05:03.934
THEN WHY ARE YOU
 COVERING YOUR EYE?

05:03.934 --> 05:07.878
I´M JUST CRYING BECAUSE I´M
 UPSET ABOUT BEING ACCUSED.

05:07.878 --> 05:10.611
BUT YOU´RE ONLY CRYING
 OUT OF ONE EYE.

05:10.611 --> 05:13.644
I´M NOT THAT UPSET.

05:13.644 --> 05:15.045
I´M NOT LYING.

05:15.045 --> 05:18.389
THE PEEPHOLE´S GOT TO BE
 ON THAT WALL SOMEWHERE.

05:18.389 --> 05:19.890
SEE! THERE IT IS!

05:19.890 --> 05:21.492
OKAY, CARMEN, RELAX.

05:21.492 --> 05:24.054
YOU PROBABLY CAN´T EVEN SEE
 ANYTHING THROUGH IT.

05:24.054 --> 05:25.796
OH, HEY, OLIVIA.

05:25.796 --> 05:27.027
WHO´S THAT?

05:27.027 --> 05:28.899
IT´S MR. LOPEZ.

05:28.899 --> 05:32.032
I WAS JUST WONDERING IF YOU
 WANTED TO STAY FOR DINNER.

05:32.032 --> 05:35.035
SURE, BUT I´M
 A VEGETARIAN.

05:35.035 --> 05:38.839
WELL, WE´LL SEE WHAT WE
 CAN DO, ALL RIGHT?

05:38.839 --> 05:40.541
YOU LITTLE FREAK.

05:40.541 --> 05:43.113
I CAN´T BELIEVE YOU WERE PEEKING
 AT ME THROUGH A HOLE.

05:43.113 --> 05:44.545
I HAVEN´T PEEKED AT YOU.

05:44.545 --> 05:46.477
THAT´S NOT WHAT THE HOLE
 WAS FOR.

05:46.477 --> 05:48.018
THEN WHAT WAS IT FOR?

05:48.018 --> 05:52.052
I PUT MY BUTT UP AGAINST IT SO I
 COULD GAS YOU OUT.

05:52.052 --> 05:56.457
YOU COULD HAVE TOLD ME THAT
 BEFORE I PUT MY EYE UP THERE.

05:57.628 --> 05:59.460
SO WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO?

05:59.460 --> 06:00.961
MAX, WHAT DID YOU SEE?

06:00.961 --> 06:02.433
NOTHING.

06:02.433 --> 06:04.435
OKAY, YOU KNOW
 THIS IS WRONG, RIGHT?

06:04.435 --> 06:06.537
OKAY, GO WASH OUT YOUR EYE.
 VAMANOS!

06:08.439 --> 06:09.940
THAT´S IT?

06:09.940 --> 06:12.503
"GO WASH YOUR EYE OUT"?

06:12.503 --> 06:14.645
MAX DOESN´T KNOW ANY BETTER.
 HE´S A LITTLE BOY.

06:14.645 --> 06:16.607
BUT YOU COULD HAVE
 BLINDED HIM.

06:16.607 --> 06:18.749
WHO KNOWS WHAT´S IN THAT FRUITY
 TEEN PERFUME YOU WEAR.

06:18.749 --> 06:20.781
THEY DON´T TEST THESE ON
 ANIMALS ANYMORE.

06:20.781 --> 06:22.683
WE DON´T KNOW IF
 THEY´RE SAFE.

06:22.683 --> 06:24.455
I WISH I WOULD HAVE
 BLINDED HIM.

06:24.455 --> 06:26.417
HE WOULDN´T BE ABLE TO
 PEEK ANYMORE.

06:26.417 --> 06:28.419
NOBODY HURTS ANYBODY
 IN THIS HOUSE.

06:28.419 --> 06:30.020
NO TELEPHONE FOR A WEEK.

06:30.020 --> 06:32.563
HE WAS LOOKING AT MY FRIEND
 GETTING UNDRESSED,

06:32.563 --> 06:34.094
AND YOU´RE PUNISHING ME?

06:34.094 --> 06:36.396
YOU WANT MORE PUNISHMENT?
 KEEP TALKING.

06:36.396 --> 06:37.027
DEFEND THE LITTLE PERV.

06:37.027 --> 06:38.799
WHAT IS GOING ON?

06:38.799 --> 06:41.702
MAX TRIED TO SEE OLIVIA NAKED,
 AND DAD´S PUNISHING ME.

06:41.702 --> 06:44.675
SOME MAN YOU MARRIED.

06:44.675 --> 06:46.937
MAX MADE A LITTLE PEEPHOLE
 IN THE WALL,

06:46.937 --> 06:48.739
BUT HE DIDN´T SEE ANYTHING.

06:48.739 --> 06:50.010
I HANDLED IT.

06:50.010 --> 06:51.141
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

06:51.141 --> 06:52.743
I TOLD HIM IT WAS WRONG.

06:52.743 --> 06:54.915
WELL, I HOPE
 YOU ALSO TOLD HIM

06:54.915 --> 06:58.689
IT WAS COMPLETELY OUT OF LINE
 AND UNACCEPTABLE BEHAVIOR

06:58.689 --> 07:02.422
AND THAT PEEKING AT SOMEONE IS
 A VIOLATION OF THEIR PRIVACY

07:02.422 --> 07:04.555
AND SHOWS A TOTAL
 LACK OF RESPECT.

07:04.555 --> 07:08.629
YEAH, LIKE THAT
 BUT STRONGER.

07:08.629 --> 07:10.701
I´M GONNA TALK TO MAX.
 THIS IS SERIOUS.

07:10.701 --> 07:13.504
COME ON, ANGIE. DON´T MAKE
 THIS BIGGER THAN IT IS.

07:13.504 --> 07:15.536
YOU´RE NOT A BOY.
 YOU WOULDN´T UNDERSTAND.

07:15.536 --> 07:16.967
HE´S STARTING TO GET CURIOUS.

07:16.967 --> 07:19.169
I DID THE SAME THING
 WHEN I WAS HIS AGE.

07:19.169 --> 07:20.511
WHO´D YOU PEEK AT?

07:20.511 --> 07:23.474
ERNIE´S MOM.

07:23.474 --> 07:27.147
OH, MY GOD.
 SHE´S A BIG WOMAN.

07:27.147 --> 07:29.049
I SAW ONE BOOB THROUGH
 ONE WINDOW

07:29.049 --> 07:31.622
AND ONE BOOB THROUGH
 THE OTHER WINDOW.

08:04.755 --> 08:09.590
HEAR YOU GOT YOURSELF
 A PEEPER.

08:09.590 --> 08:11.592
CARMEN CAME CRYING
 TO YOU, TOO, HUH?

08:11.592 --> 08:13.263
YOU KNOW WHAT REALLY HAPPENED?

08:13.263 --> 08:14.765
MAX IS GROWING UP.

08:14.765 --> 08:16.567
HE´LL SOON UNDERSTAND

08:16.567 --> 08:18.829
WHY IT´S OKAY THAT
 ANNA KOURNIKOVA NEVER WINS.

08:18.829 --> 08:21.231
YOU KNOW, IT´S ABOUT TIME.

08:21.231 --> 08:22.933
HEY, WHAT HAPPENED?

08:22.933 --> 08:26.176
MAX GOT CAUGHT SNEAKING A LOOK
 AT ONE OF CARMEN´S FRIENDS.

08:26.176 --> 08:27.838
OH, MAN.

08:27.838 --> 08:31.141
I DIDN´T SEE MY FIRST NAKED
 WOMAN UNTIL I WAS 18...

08:31.141 --> 08:34.845
AND THE FIRST ONE THAT WAS
 AWAKE UNTIL I WAS 30.

08:34.845 --> 08:37.688
YOU KNOW, I CAUGHT GEORGE
 PEEKING AT A WOMAN

08:37.688 --> 08:39.620
WHEN HE WAS AROUND MAX´S AGE.

08:39.620 --> 08:41.121
YOU REMEMBER THAT GEORGE?

08:41.121 --> 08:45.255
I THINK ERNIE WOULD LIKE TO
 HEAR THAT STORY.

08:45.255 --> 08:46.627
HUH?

08:46.627 --> 08:49.529
NO, HE WOULDN´T, MOM.

08:49.529 --> 08:51.101
GEORGE, I FORGET.

08:51.101 --> 08:52.663
WHO WAS THAT AGAIN?

08:52.663 --> 08:55.135
YOU KNOW, I DON´T REMEMBER.
 BACK TO WORK, MOM.

08:55.135 --> 08:58.739
WAS IT THAT SUPERFOX SYLVIA
 FROM ACROSS THE STREET?

08:58.739 --> 09:01.612
NO, BUT IT WAS A FORM
 OF WILDLIFE.

09:03.714 --> 09:05.145
WELL, WHO WAS IT?

09:05.145 --> 09:07.547
YOUR MOM.

09:10.150 --> 09:11.782
OH, NO!

09:11.782 --> 09:15.956
HOW COULD YOU PEEP
 AT MY MOM, GEORGE?

09:15.956 --> 09:17.928
ERNIE, I WASN´T TRYING
 TO, MAN.

09:17.928 --> 09:20.160
WHO WATCHES TV NAKED
 AFTER A SHOWER?

09:20.160 --> 09:23.163
SHE LIKES TO AIR-DRY.

09:24.765 --> 09:27.037
LOOK, TO EVEN THINGS UP,

09:27.037 --> 09:30.701
I´LL LET YOU LOOK AT
 MY MOM NAKED.

09:32.272 --> 09:35.746
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

09:39.850 --> 09:42.713
SO, YOU WANT PICTURES
 OR THE REAL THING?

09:42.713 --> 09:44.014
[ LAUGHS ]

09:50.120 --> 09:52.693
WHAT HOSPITAL IS HE AT?
 I´LL BE RIGHT THERE.

09:52.693 --> 09:54.094
WHAT IS IT?

09:54.094 --> 09:56.096
THEY´RE TAKING MAX
 TO THE HOSPITAL.

09:56.096 --> 09:57.968
HE GOT INTO A FIGHT
 AT SCHOOL.

09:57.968 --> 09:59.800
A FIGHT, TOO?

09:59.800 --> 10:03.734
WOW, WHEN THAT KIDS HUEVOS
 DROP, IT´S LIKE THUNDER.

10:09.339 --> 10:10.681
MAX, ARE YOU OKAY?

10:10.681 --> 10:12.282
HE FELL AND HIT HIS HEAD.

10:12.282 --> 10:13.914
THEY PUT 10 STITCHES IN,

10:13.914 --> 10:16.046
BUT THERE´S NO FRACTURE
 OR CONCUSSION.

10:16.046 --> 10:18.018
I GOT INTO A FIGHT
 WITH FIVE GUYS.

10:18.018 --> 10:20.651
YOU SHOULD HAVE SEEN THEM, DAD.
 THEY WERE SCARED.

10:20.651 --> 10:22.092
YOU PUT UP A GOOD FIGHT?

10:22.092 --> 10:24.855
NO. WHEN THEY SAW ALL THE BLOOD
 COMING OUT OF MY HEAD,

10:24.855 --> 10:26.697
THEY WERE SCARED.

10:26.697 --> 10:30.230
THIS IS WHY THOSE BOYS
 WERE PICKING ON HIM.

10:30.230 --> 10:32.302
SOMEBODY PUT UP A PICTURE
 OF MAX SLEEPING

10:32.302 --> 10:34.765
ON THE CURRENT-EVENTS BOARD
 AT HIS SCHOOL.

10:34.765 --> 10:37.167
YOU FIGHT WITH GUYS,
 YOU PEEP ON GIRLS,

10:37.167 --> 10:40.871
YOU SLEEP IN YOUR UNDERWEAR
 WITH A LITTLE PINK BUNNY.

10:42.142 --> 10:45.275
YOU´RE A COMPLEX
 LITTLE MAN, MAX.

10:45.275 --> 10:47.417
I DIDN´T SLEEP
 WITH THE BUNNY.

10:47.417 --> 10:48.919
CARMEN PUT IT THERE.

10:48.919 --> 10:51.051
DAD, EVERYONE AT SCHOOL
 SAW THAT PICTURE.

10:51.051 --> 10:52.422
I´M GONNA KILL HER.

10:52.422 --> 10:53.824
MAX, PLEASE.

10:53.824 --> 10:55.425
NO, I´M REALLY GONNA
 KILL HER.

10:55.425 --> 10:58.388
AND GRANDMA TOLD ME HOW TO MAKE
 IT LOOK LIKE AN ACCIDENT.

11:00.130 --> 11:02.092
YOU´RE NOT KILLING ANYONE.

11:02.092 --> 11:06.296
AND NOW YOU KNOW HOW IT FEELS TO
 HAVE YOUR PRIVACY INVADED.

11:07.738 --> 11:10.440
MAX, I GOT YOU SOME
 PUDDING FROM THE CAFETERIA.

11:12.803 --> 11:13.904
OKAY, COME HERE.

11:17.748 --> 11:19.750
THIS IS THE WORST
 THING YOU´VE EVER DONE.

11:19.750 --> 11:22.753
YOUR BROTHER´S IN A HOSPITAL
 WITH STITCHES BECAUSE OF YOU.

11:22.753 --> 11:24.815
I JUST WANTED
 TO TEACH HIM A LESSON.

11:24.815 --> 11:26.256
I DIDN´T KNOW HE´D GET HURT.

11:26.256 --> 11:29.960
I´M NOT WORRIED ABOUT HIS HEAD.
 THAT´LL HEAL.

11:29.960 --> 11:31.792
NOBODY´S EVER GONNA
 FORGET THAT PICTURE.

11:31.792 --> 11:33.864
EVERY TIME HE WALKS DOWN
 THE HALL AT SCHOOL,

11:33.864 --> 11:35.996
THEY´RE GONNA BE CALLING HIM
 A SISSY AND A WUSS

11:35.996 --> 11:37.768
AND A BUNNY HUGGER.

11:38.969 --> 11:42.202
Max: I CAN HEAR YOU!

11:42.202 --> 11:44.104
MAYBE YOU DIDN´T
 UNDERSTAND ME

11:44.104 --> 11:46.106
WHEN I SAID NOBODY HURTS
 ANYBODY IN THIS FAMILY,

11:46.106 --> 11:47.838
SO LET ME MAKE IT CLEARER.

11:47.838 --> 11:49.980
NO PHONE, NO E-MAIL, AND
 NO TV FOR A MONTH.

11:49.980 --> 11:51.742
I´M GETTING
 MORE PUNISHMENTS?

11:51.742 --> 11:54.044
WHY DO I EVEN TALK TO YOU?
 YOU ALWAYS TAKE MAX´S SIDE.

11:54.044 --> 11:55.946
HE´S THE GOLDEN CHILD.

11:55.946 --> 11:57.717
HEY, DON´T WALK AWAY
 FROM ME.

11:57.717 --> 11:59.790
WHY? YOU DON´T NEED ME.
 YOU´VE GOT MAX.

11:59.790 --> 12:02.122
YOU LOVE HIM MORE THAN YOU
 LOVE ME ANYWAY.

12:06.296 --> 12:09.860
WE REALLY ARE BETTER OFF
 WITHOUT HER.

12:21.011 --> 12:23.113
DID ANGIE BRING CARMEN
 HOME YET?

12:23.113 --> 12:24.744
NO.

12:24.744 --> 12:27.147
HEY, MAX.
 IS YOUR HEAD OKAY?

12:27.147 --> 12:30.750
HOW MANY BEERS AM I
 HOLDING UP, HONEY?

12:31.982 --> 12:34.024
YOU NEVER CALLED ME HONEY.

12:34.024 --> 12:36.086
WELL, YOU SHOULD HAVE
 BEEN CUTER.

12:38.158 --> 12:40.330
CARMEN --

12:40.330 --> 12:41.792
OH.

12:41.792 --> 12:42.893
WHAT´S GOING ON?

12:42.893 --> 12:44.094
NOTHING, BENNY.

12:44.094 --> 12:46.396
DAD LOVES ME
 MORE THAN CARMEN.

12:46.396 --> 12:48.038
MAX, THAT´S NOT TRUE.

12:48.038 --> 12:49.900
OKAY, DAD.

12:51.371 --> 12:54.244
CAN YOU GIVE US SOME PRIVACY?
 I NEED TO TALK TO GEORGE.

12:55.846 --> 12:59.209
ANGIE, I KNOW WHERE YOU´RE
 GOING ON THIS,

12:59.209 --> 13:01.982
AND I WANT YOU TO KNOW
 THAT I AM ON YOUR SIDE.

13:01.982 --> 13:03.113
THANK YOU.

13:03.113 --> 13:05.285
THEN YOU CAN STAY.

13:06.987 --> 13:08.859
[ NO AUDIO ]

13:18.028 --> 13:19.529
AS FOR YOU, MISTER --

13:19.529 --> 13:21.902
ANGIE, I KNOW WHERE YOU´RE
 GOING WITH THIS,

13:21.902 --> 13:24.274
AND I WANT YOU TO KNOW THAT
 I´M ON YOUR SIDE, TOO.

13:24.274 --> 13:26.276
SO LET´S EAT QUIETLY.
 SHH!

13:28.308 --> 13:30.510
I JUST HAD A LONG TALK
 WITH CARMEN.

13:30.510 --> 13:33.383
I THINK YOU´RE BEING COMPLETELY
 UNFAIR WITH HER.

13:33.383 --> 13:35.545
MAN, SHE WRAPS YOU AROUND
 HER LITTLE FINGER.

13:35.545 --> 13:38.818
SHE CAN´T DO THAT TO ME ´CAUSE I
 DON´T BUY INTO ALL THAT DRAMA.

13:38.818 --> 13:42.052
THAT´S NOT DRAMA, GEORGE.
 THOSE ARE HER REAL FEELINGS.

13:42.052 --> 13:43.854
BUT EVERY DAY?

13:43.854 --> 13:45.896
WHO FEELS EVERY DAY?

13:45.896 --> 13:47.257
SHE´S A TEENAGE GIRL.

13:47.257 --> 13:49.029
THIS IS THE WORST PART
 OF HER LIFE.

13:49.029 --> 13:51.461
MAX IS A 10-YEAR-OLD BOY
 WITHOUT A CARE IN THE WORLD.

13:51.461 --> 13:53.363
OF COURSE YOU LIKE
 HIM BETTER.

13:53.363 --> 13:56.166
SO YOU DO, TOO?
 NOW WE CAN SAY IT OUT LOUD.

13:56.166 --> 13:58.038
MAKE THAT THREE.

13:58.038 --> 13:59.239
NO!

14:00.440 --> 14:02.472
IT´S JUST THAT HE´S EASIER
 RIGHT NOW.

